title: News24.com | Court rejects bid to compel govt to fix 'dire state' of education
text: News24.com | Court rejects bid to compel govt to fix 'dire state' of education Friday, 18 September 2015 (6 minutes ago) The Western Cape High Court has dismissed a bid to compel the government to fix the "dire state" of basic education .
